      "review": "This is a location inside the Food Lab. I am still trying to figure out if this is a pop up or a permanent stand. They have their main location in the heart of San Bernadino.\n\nThe food was hot and fresh, I saw the guy cook it with my own two eyes and I was satisfied with his cooking technique. The staff need to have a mildly slightly better way of notifying the call out person that the food is done because they didn't notice it was done for a solid 2 minutes. It was funny and I didn't mind but if I was starving I'd be hangry.\n\nGood times surrounded this food trip, I will return.",
